				\begin{document}
$$\displaystyle \begin{aligned} \begin{array}{rcl} U_{sum} & =&\displaystyle \sum_{i=1}^n \frac{C_i}{T_i} \leq n (2^{1/n}-1) {} \end{array} \end{aligned} $$
\end{document} Figure 6.12 shows the bound of constraint (6.7).Fig. 6.12
Bound of constraint (6.7)

 The bound is about 0.7 for large n: 6.8limn→∞n∗(21∕n−1)=loge(2)=ln(2)≈0.7\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
